This is the data management repository for the year 2026.

entry_smc.py: (the code that can fill entry excel(sample database) automatically
entries_CMMR.py: is used for filling in database for data of CMMR2023
folder "entry" : file name with 1, 2, 3, ..., 308 (There are 246 files in SMC2024, 62 files in CMMR2023)
sample_database_SMC2024_filled: the finish excel for smc2024 (可以基於這份接下去填完其他資料夾的檔案)
database.xlsx: the finished excel with SMC2024, CMMR2023